title: ‘The Challenge: All Stars’ Season 2, Episode 5 With Brad | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
The 'Challenge’ legend Brad Fiorenza joins Johnny this week to talk about his run on ‘All Stars’ Season 2, how the game has changed since they started on the show, the best prizes they ever won, Episode 5 of ‘All Stars,’ and much more.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Brad Fiorenza
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
Additional Production: Juliet Litman
